///     * PDM Port registers - This section is consolidated registers for 8 channel PDM.
///     ###
///     # # ----------------------------------------------------------
///     @ 0x00000 CTRL1                (P)
///               %unsigned 4  CLKDIV                    0x4
///                                    ###
///                                    * DSD CLKOUT Divider.
